---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Dev Error DB"
  description="Contact Dev Error DB with corrections, feedback, or suggestions for missing developer error troubleshooting pages."
>
  <section class="content-page">
    <h1>Contact Dev Error DB</h1>
    <p>
      If you notice an error page that needs a correction, have feedback on an
      existing troubleshooting guide, or want to suggest a missing developer
      error, email us at
      <a href="mailto:contact@dev-error-db.com">contact@dev-error-db.com</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Helpful reports include the exact error message, the tool or platform
      involved, and any safe, non-secret context about when the error appears.
      Do not send API keys, tokens, passwords, private repository contents, or
      other sensitive credentials.
    </p>
    <h2>Correction requests</h2>
    <p>
      For corrections, include the page URL, the exact section that appears
      wrong or outdated, the expected correction, and any public documentation,
      issue, release note, or reproducible context that supports the change.
    </p>
    <h2>Source and privacy boundaries</h2>
    <p>
      Dev Error DB cannot use private logs, customer data, secrets, or
      unsupported claims as public evidence. Public source links are preferred,
      and sensitive material should be redacted before contact.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
